quran[29{c,v,t}:
91,1,Wash shamsi wa duhaa haa
91,2,Wal qamari izaa talaa haa
91,3,Wannahaari izaa jallaa haa
91,4,Wallaili izaa yaghshaa haa
91,5,Wassamaaa'i wa maa banaahaa
91,6,Wal ardi wa maa tahaahaa
91,7,Wa nafsinw wa maa sawwaahaa
91,8,Fa-alhamahaa fujoorahaa wa taqwaahaa
91,9,Qad aflaha man zakkaahaa
91,10,Wa qad khaaba man dassaahaa
91,11,Kazzabat Samoodu bi taghwaahaaa
91,12,Izim ba'asa ashqaahaa
91,13,Faqaala lahum Rasoolul laahi naaqatal laahi wa suqiyaahaa
91,14,Fakazzaboohu fa'aqaroohaa fadamdama 'alaihim Rabbuhum bizambihim fasaw waahaa
91,15,Wa laa yakhaafu'uqbaahaa
92,1,Wallaili izaa yaghshaa
92,2,Wannahaari izaa tajalla
92,3,Wa maa khalaqaz zakara wal unthaa
92,4,Inna sa'yakum lashattaa
92,5,Fa ammaa man a'taa wattaqaa
92,6,Wa saddaqa bil husnaa
92,7,Fasanu yassiruhoo lilyusraa
92,8,Wa ammaa mam bakhila wastaghnaa
92,9,Wa kazzaba bil husnaa
92,10,Fasanu yassiruhoo lil'usraa
92,11,Wa maa yughnee 'anhu maaluhooo izaa taraddaa
92,12,Inna 'alainaa lal hudaa
92,13,Wa inna lanaa lal Aakhirata wal oolaa
92,14,Fa anzartukum naaran talazzaa
